{
  "stem": "14613.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As you have seen, I went through ghetto Auschwitz, other things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in a way, considered everything else after the war, I came here with nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went to school, went to university, went into business.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And some people may say, you accomplished a lot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That may be so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But therefore, I feel that after what I went through, I should give back something to the society that I received.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And therefore, I feel that it is important for us to-- it's what I have instilled in my children, I hope-- not to be a bystander.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I think the atrocities which happened, happened because of what I call, the world stood by and did nothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the world is a big world.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The world consists of individuals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And therefore, it is important that individuals do things, that individuals be involved and get involved.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in a way, this is the reason why I have decided to do something, to give to others that maybe are less fortunate.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So yes, I am involved in various projects.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am involved in projects of keeping the memory of the Holocaust alive, so that maybe the new generation can learn something from it, so that it will not be repeated again.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I am involved in [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] helping the righteous Gentiles, the few individuals that saved the Jewish life during the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I think they are the perfect example.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That even among the most horrible circumstances, the people that are moral and ethical, they can do something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, there were very few righteous Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But therefore, they are so important.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because their example shows us what can be done, if people care.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
